<font color="#FF0000">SUPER COOL AND COLD!</font><br>
<tt>Sun Sep 14 14:25:28 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I didn't wear sissy sunglasses... had the upper part of my cheekbones tattoed black.. like a bad ass linebacker.<br>
Didn't wear clothes either.. just my P-38 and a steel jock strap.. deeply blued and lightly oiled.<br>
Didn't wear a watch either... just looked at the sun like Crocodile Dundee...(ran out of fuel alot during the monsoons!  Also, late for chow!)<br>
I didn't know you back then.. I'm glad I didn't.  You are the kind who would have penetrated my veneer of numbness.  I would have feared for your life.  Probably would have flown into a tree admiring your shoulder holstered .38 cal (needed one to shoot F-U lizards off the ceiling of my hooch.)<br>
Fact of the matter is... I know you now.  If they mess with you.. they mess with me.  If they mess with me.. they'll end up learning impaired, walking impaired and talking impaired!<br>
If your Frilly Five are as tough as my thirteen year old... well, I'm always available for one more rescue mission.  Problem is.. candy don't work no more... need pocket full of large denomination bills!<br><br>
Am honored to have your book (do the crayons come with it?) I will send you one of mine if you back mail your address... I'll even provide a tutor to help you with the big words.<br><br>
Mustang Two Four - Humping through some hard times.
